" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN4可以既 N4大概你要識得同日本人講野<br />\n識問路 叫野食埋單 問貨品detail之類 問人拎野之類<br />\n好似at least個文法程度去到識用 これをもらってもいいですか？ 再後D就考得 唔太記得</blockquote><br />\n仲有仲有 助詞要識解識用最少8成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我果陣唔識呢D搞到差D奶野"},{"pid":"f82a5a938b2e7d2d9744bdbb49d8ecea8dd02209","tid":158133,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇地方係日本人教日文? 唔太貴既</blockquote><br />\npasona全日本人<br />\n有d係香港住得耐少少既聽得明中文既<br />\n有d日本過來教一年半載既剩係聽得明英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb796f0658f817ee39f2b6df24c38bc247c6fd05","tid":158133,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"借位講下灣仔校: 姓劉個阿sir 好煩; 姓鄧個miss都麻麻; 姓莫個miss教得幾好但我唔鍾意佢啲態度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42e3af936d0ff7afdf9bd677eb8ee4c5c4c881c","tid":158133,"uid":7359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想上堂唔悶跟 Ray Lo <br />\n利申：讀緊 N1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢成日なるほど XD<br />\n同埋一唔小心就吹水吹勁耐<br />\n<br />\n上年讀完深造3 而家無所事事好想讀多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好掛住Ray Lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> n4個時佢教 <br />\ndse之後甩左<br />\n呢架想跟番都無機會<br />\n只教深造</blockquote><br />\n係咪耶穌?</blockquote><br />\nray lo<br />\n果陣翻工甩咗有d 後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46726e99de1afd866224d1cd890809f97e7ad32b","tid":158133,"uid":7376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借位講下灣仔校: 姓劉個阿sir 好煩; 姓鄧個miss都麻麻; 姓莫個miss教得幾好但我唔鍾意佢啲態度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以詳細啲講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0a56d9a97c6b356e47cac473625487b86e3f79","tid":158133,"uid":3535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要讀到幾多先可以考n5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好哂錢啦N5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁n4呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN4可以既 N4大概你要識得同日本人講野<br />\n識問路 叫野食埋單 問貨品detail之類 問人拎野之類<br />\n好似at least個文法程度去到識用 これをもらってもいいですか？ 再後D就考得 唔太記得</blockquote><br />\n仲有仲有 助詞要識解識用最少8成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我果陣唔識呢D搞到差D奶野</blockquote><br />\n咁我諗要讀多年先穩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5f0c5a61d615350794a77b5b1629712d4e1636","tid":158133,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>借位講下灣仔校: 姓劉個阿sir 好煩; 姓鄧個miss都麻麻; 姓莫個miss教得幾好但我唔鍾意佢啲態度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以詳細啲講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姓劉嗰個阿sir 上堂好似教緊小學咁, 所以我覺得上佢堂好煩, 好幾次我遲1個鐘到都仲未複習完上堂啲野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姓鄧嗰個我覺得麻麻地, 進度好似有啲慢, 又太跟書<br />\n<br />\n姓莫嗰個就有料到嘅, 但鍾意&ldquo;屈&rdquo; 啲學生, 例如佢get 唔到個學生問咩佢會話 &ldquo;你係指xxx係咪? 點會係咁架, 係xxx架嘛! &rdquo; 但其實個學生唔係想問呢樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c5b55b6868a77dbc741353b9b4089c09d15d7f","tid":158133,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要讀到幾多先可以考n5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好哂錢啦N5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁n4呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN4可以既 N4大概你要識得同日本人講野<br />\n識問路 叫野食埋單 問貨品detail之類 問人拎野之類<br />\n好似at least個文法程度去到識用 これをもらってもいいですか？ 再後D就考得 唔太記得</blockquote><br />\n仲有仲有 助詞要識解識用最少8成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我果陣唔識呢D搞到差D奶野</blockquote><br />\n咁我諗要讀多年先穩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴線我朋友兩三年考左N1番黎 唔好咁哂時間 自己認真學好快上手<br />\n睇日劇 多D同識日文既研究下講下"},{"pid":"c5813b985ad4bf564ddfe0279694d4b829ed8869","tid":158133,"uid":2462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"本來上緊太子 李小姐<br />\n悶到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近轉班去左旺角唔知邊個miss<br />\n都係好悶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcc96f08299fe7012c6981984965e37f8d46e96","tid":158133,"uid":3439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想上堂唔悶跟 Ray Lo <br />\n利申：讀緊 N1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢成日なるほど XD<br />\n同埋一唔小心就吹水吹勁耐<br />\n<br />\n上年讀完深造3 而家無所事事好想讀多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好掛住Ray Lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> n4個時佢教 <br />\ndse之後甩左<br />\n呢架想跟番都無機會<br />\n只教深造</blockquote><br />\n係咪耶穌?</blockquote><br />\nray lo<br />\n果陣翻工甩咗有d 後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等陣佢再開N4班"},{"pid":"eb9f58c57119f6b377777cc2699efb4bf48b3452","tid":